How to install Steam Workshop mods on a Palworld Dedicated Server

Downloading Workshop Content via SteamCMD:

Find IDs: Go to the Palworld Steam Workshop page (steamcommunity.com/app/1623730/workshop) and find the Item or Collection ID from the URL.
Use Commands: Run steamcmd.exe again with these commands (replace IDs).

workshop_download_item <AppID_Palworld> <ItemID> 
(e.g., workshop_download_item 1623730 31241234)

workshop_download_collection <AppID_Palworld> <CollectionID> 
(e.g., workshop_download_collection 1623730 1234567890)
